{"file_name": "8.docx", "file_type": "docx", "confidence": 0.87, "time_taken": 0.08, "memory_mb": 0.16, "units": [{"type": "paragraph", "text": "*******************", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Android developer with 3 years experience", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "E-mail:", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "LinkedIn: \tPhone:**********", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Languages: English, Hebrew, Russian\tResidence: Tel Aviv, Israel", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "SKILLS", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Programming languages: Kotlin, Java, C++, Dart", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Technologies: Android SDK, Android NDK, Android Architecture Components, Embedded programming, Kotlin Coroutines, RxJava2, Dagger2, Koin, Retrofit2, OkHttp, Google Maps API, Picasso, Material Design, REST API, Joda-Time, Gson, Flutter, JSON, HTML5, CSS3, XML, QT, DOORS, MKS.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "IDE: Android Studio, , IntelliJ IDEA, Eclipse, WebStorm", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Used principles: Clean architecture, MVVM Pattern, MVP Pattern", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Version control system: Git, Mercurial", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Agile: JIRA", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Databases: SQLite", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "PROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "2019 \u2013 present | Inetex LTD (Israel, Rehovot) |", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Android Developer", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Project: Android application for multiplatform car rental portal ilCarro. It allows people all over Israel share their private cars to others for a limited period or time with an affordable price for clients. Mobile client offers full functionality of the portal, making the searching and booking processes easier and available from anywhere.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Area of responsibility \u2013 developing application from scratch, fixing problems, adding and testing new features, code deployment.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Technologies:  RxJava2, LiveData, MVVM pattern, Clean Architecture, Dagger2, Retrofit2, OkHttp, Google Maps, Cloudinary API, Picasso, Gson.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "2017 \u2013 2019 | NTC Astrosoft MIR (Saint Petersburg, Russia) |", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Android Developer", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Project: Mobile platform for AUDI E-Tron. It is based on Android OS and provides all needed information about car state to the driver and gives him control of several systems. (remote control, car alarm system etc.)", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Area of responsibility \u2013 refactoring existing code base, participating in embedded controlling system development, implementing and testing new functionalities, requirements checking, code deployment.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Technologies: Android NDK, RxJaxa2, Dagger2, Retrofit2, JSON, MVP pattern, CMake, DOORS, MKS.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Project: Mobile system for malfunction detection module of gas turbine engine of military ship.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "System is based on Android OS and allows operators to observe and control all parameters of working gas turbine engine anywhere in the ship accelerating malfunction detection process.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Area of responsibility \u2013 participating in developing and refactoring code base, fixing problems, code deployment.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Technologies: Android NDK, C++, RxJaxa2, Dagger2, Retrofit2, JSON, MVP pattern, MVVM pattern, QNX, NPS, QT, CMake, DOORS, MKS", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "EDUCATION 2017 \u2013 2019 | Saint Petersburg Electrotechnical University, Master\u2019s degree of Computer Engineering Technology", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Recommendations are available upon request.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "textbox", "text": "*******************", "confidence": 0.85, "metadata": {}}, {"type": "textbox", "text": "Android developer with 3 years experience", "confidence": 0.85, "metadata": {}}, {"type": "textbox", "text": "E-mail:", "confidence": 0.85, "metadata": {}}, {"type": "textbox", "text": "LinkedIn:", "confidence": 0.85, "metadata": {}}, {"type": "textbox", "text": "Phone:**********", "confidence": 0.85, "metadata": {}}, {"type": "textbox", "text": "Languages: English, Hebrew, Russian", "confidence": 0.85, "metadata": {}}, {"type": "textbox", "text": "Residence: Tel Aviv, Israel", "confidence"